description:
This is the additional puzzle pack for "Jigsaw Masterpieces". The following 10 puzzle images are included.
-Kazusa Sea Route
-Noborito Bay
-Nihonbashi bridge in Edo
-The village of Sekiya on the Sumida River
-Hakone Lake in Sagami Province
-Mount Fuji reflects in Lake Kawaguchi, seen from the Misaka Pass in Kai Province
-Hodogoya on the Tokaido
-A sketch of the Mitsui shop in Suruga in Edo
-Sunset across the Ry≈çgoku bridge from the bank of the Sumida River at Onmayagashi
-Sazai hall - Temple of Five Hundred Rakan
name: Masterpieces of World  - Ukiyo-e, Hokusai's Thirty-Six Views of Mt.Fuji Vol.3-
